23 nurse-coordinated program if such program is licensed pursuant to
24 the provisions of the Uniform Controlled Dangerous Substances Act.
SENATE FLOOR VERSION - SB1257 SFLR Page 10
(Bold face denotes Committee Amendments)

1 A ho spice program offers palliative and supportive care to meet the
2 special needs arising out of the physical, emotional and spiritual
3 stresses which are experienced during the final stages of illness
