5 four (24) hours a day, seven (7) days a week, and is provided on the
6 basis of need, regardless of ability to pay. “Class A” Hospice
7 refers to Medicare-certified hospices. “Class B” refers to all
8 other providers of hospice services;
9 25. “Imitation controlled substance” means a substance that is
